title: Asustor AS6602T NAS Storage
description: The Asustor AS6602T NAS Storage is a high-performance network-attached storage device that comes with a variety of features and capabilities to support advanced storage requirements. It is designed to offer reliable data storage, fast data transfer speeds, and a range of backup and virtualization solutions. The device features two 2.5 GbE ports, which can support up to 5 Gbps under Link Aggregation. This makes it easy to transfer data quickly and efficiently, even when dealing with large files. Additionally, it has dual M.2 NVMe SSD ports, which can be used for fast caching, allowing for even faster access to frequently accessed files. The Asustor AS6602T is optimized for 4K video playback, offering an overwhelming 4K experience.
